title: 09/30: Week 4 Recap - Michel, Trubisky and More (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
How about Mitchell Trubisky (2:00)!? Was he that good or was his opponent that bad? And we've got our Week 4 winners (8:15) like Kerryon Johnson, Sony Michel and Corey Davis and losers (16:00) such as Jamaal Williams and Jordan Howard ... Big news to know about (23:00), Buy or Sell (27:12) with Larry Fitzgerald, Aaron Rodgers, Calvin Ridley and more, plus a look at the leaderboard at QB (36:30), RB (40:00), WR (41:10) and TE (42:35) ... Recapping every game with our Fantasy thoughts (46:22) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
